    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Buildings that are ornamental or functional, usually of light construction; may be designed as temporary. Uses include for shelter, refreshment, entertainment, or recreation. Examples may be found in a park, world's fair, seaside, adjacent to a sports field, or in a group of buildings.</Note_Text>
